### DevFinder API - Test Requests
###
### Use with REST Client extension (VS Code) or copy/paste to curl

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/v1
@token = 

### =====================================================
### APP INFO
### =====================================================

### @name get_app_info
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### =====================================================
### DEV ENDPOINTS
### =====================================================

### @name list_devs
GET {{baseUrl}}/devs?page=1

###

### @name get_dev_by_username
GET {{baseUrl}}/devs/marcelovilela

###

### @name create_dev
POST {{baseUrl}}/devs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "marcelovilela",
  "name": "Marcelo Vilela",
  "avatar": "https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/marcelovilela",
  "bio": "Full-stack developer passionate about clean code"
}

###

### @name get_me
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### @name get_dev_likes
GET {{baseUrl}}/devs/marcelovilela/likes

###

### @name like_dev
POST {{baseUrl}}/devs/otheruser/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### @name unlike_dev
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/devs/otheruser/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### @name dislike_dev
POST {{baseUrl}}/devs/otheruser/dislike
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### @name undislike_dev
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/devs/otheruser/dislike
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### =====================================================
### CHANNEL ENDPOINTS
### =====================================================

### @name list_channels
GET {{baseUrl}}/channels?page=1

###

### @name get_channel_by_name
GET {{baseUrl}}/channels/Rocketseat

###

### @name create_channel
POST {{baseUrl}}/channels
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Rocketseat",
  "link": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSfwM5u0Kce6Cce8_S72olg",
  "category": "Desenvolvimento Front-End",
  "description": "O canal da Rocketseat lotado de conteudo para pessoas desenvolvedoras.",
  "tags": ["javascript", "react", "react native"]
}

###

### @name like_channel
POST {{baseUrl}}/channels/1/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### @name unlike_channel
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/channels/1/like
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### @name follow_channel
POST {{baseUrl}}/channels/1/follow
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### @name refresh_channels
POST {{baseUrl}}/channels/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### =====================================================
### VIDEO ENDPOINTS
### =====================================================

### @name list_videos
GET {{baseUrl}}/videos?page=1

###

### @name get_video_by_id
GET {{baseUrl}}/video/1

###

### @name create_video
POST {{baseUrl}}/video
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "React Patterns",
  "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dQw4w9WgXcQ",
  "channel": "Rocketseat",
  "channel_url": "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSfwM5u0Kce6Cce8_S72olg",
  "thumbnail": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/dQw4w9WgXcQ/hqdefault.jpg",
  "channel_id": "1",
  "viewnum": 15000
}

###

### @name get_trending_videos
GET {{baseUrl}}/trending?page=1

###

### @name get_subscription_videos
GET {{baseUrl}}/subscriptions?page=1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### @name refresh_video
POST {{baseUrl}}/video/1/refresh
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
